---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#332211] text-[#eaddd0] py-12 border-t border-[#443322]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-3">NF COFFEE</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#c8b7a6]">Menyajikan cita rasa kopi autentik dari biji pilihan pilihan langsung ke cangkir Anda.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Jam Operasional</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#c8b7a6]">Setiap Hari: 09.00 - 22.00 WITA</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Kontak & Lokasi</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#c8b7a6]">Makassar, Sulawesi Selatan</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[#443322] text-center text-xs text-[#a69584]">
    &copy; {currentYear} NF Coffee. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</footer>